snippet.title: Johnny Depp traumatised after almost losing his finger by abuser Amber Heard...
snippet.description: see how it affected him emotionally in a Black Mass press conference back in 2015... this was about six months after Amber severed his finger back in Australia - she threw a bottle and it smashed against the tabletop and caught his finger. A recording of the bloody aftermath can be heard on incrediblyaverage channel. Depp also spoke about this in court...back then, he lied about how he was injured to protect her. To this day, the scars remain to be seen not just physically but emotionally. What scars did Amber leave with? Nothing. #justiceforjohnnydepp
